top_performing.query: SELECT product_id, normalized_shap_value, normalized_score, sku_category FROM sku_prioritization where sku_category='High';

top_performing_sku_count.query: SELECT count(distinct(product_id)) FROM sku_prioritization where sku_category='High';

all_priority_score.query: SELECT product_id, normalized_shap_value, normalized_score, sku_category FROM sku_prioritization;
